description: You'll love this bright and beautifully updated 1-bedroom plus condo in a prime South Boston location off Telegraph Hill! The kitchen features gorgeous cabinets, a farmhouse sink, stainless steel appliances, recessed lighting, and a tile backsplash, opening to a generous living room with large windows and hardwood floors. The primary bedroom is complemented by a versatile separate room, perfect for a home office, playroom, or den. The full bathroom boasts upgraded tile finishes, and there's ample thoughtful closet space solutions throughout. Conveniently located near the Red Line, buses, beach, and all the thriving retail options along West and East Broadway.
